{
  "abstract": "France was a founding member of the CGIAR in\r\n1971, and her ties to the CGIAR system are well\r\nestablished. In particular, France has a strong\r\ninterest in the agricultural development of West\r\nAfrica. ICRISAT has enjoyed support from France\r\nfor over three decades, starting with a contribution\r\nin 1979 towards the establishment of ICRISAT’s\r\nSahelian Center in Niamey, Niger. An extremely\r\nwelcome contribution was in 1996 when France\r\ncontributed additional funds to help ICRISAT tide\r\nover its financial crisis.....",
